name: Jar Jar Binks
Lore: 'Young Otolla Gungan. Clumsy. Outcast from Otoh Gunga for continually making mistakes that placed other members of Gungan society at risk.',
Text: 'May deploy to any site, even without presence or Force icons. During battle may use 1 Force to target one opponent''s character present. Both players draw destiny. If your destiny + 2 > opponent''s destiny + target''s ability, Jar Jar and target are lost.',
